<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<title>Home</title>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
	<div class="main-wrapper">
		<!-- @import "main-kit/header.kit" -->
		<div class="content-wrapper">
			<section class="about">
				<div class="title-block">
					<div class="container">
						<h2>"First, solve the problem. Then, write the code."</h2>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="content-block">
					<div class="container">
						<div class="block-item prew">
							<p class="body med">IT Hoot is an office-based team of 40 dedicated specialists. The company was
								founded by programmers for programmers with the view to create solutions for medium and large
								business. Our values are not the quantity of projects or number of employers, but
								professionalism and long-term partnership for complex projects. We are not only professional in
								writing code, but in our attitude to the working process and business partnership.</p>
							<div class="img-wrapper">
								<img width="592" height="392"
									src="https://www.meme-arsenal.com/memes/6cec25ddda4b0fd41a8c00b57113fdde.jpg" alt="">
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="block-item prew-group reverse">
							<p>Anton and Anatoly are senior developers with over 14 years of experience in programming. Four
								years ago they decided to unite talented programmers to build big scalable projects and founded
								IT Hoot. They are passionate about programming so much that they are still involved in
								developing processes even though the company uses only full-time employees..</p>
							<div class="card-group">
								<div class="card-person">
									<img width="312" height="392"
										src="https://www.meme-arsenal.com/memes/6cec25ddda4b0fd41a8c00b57113fdde.jpg" alt="">
									<div class="card-name">
										<p class="body medBolt">Name Surname, CEO</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="card-person">
									<img width="312" height="392"
										src="https://www.meme-arsenal.com/memes/6cec25ddda4b0fd41a8c00b57113fdde.jpg" alt="">
									<div class="card-name">
										<p class="body medBolt">Name Surname, CTO</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<h3 class="sub-title">How we perform work process</h3>
						<div class="block-item reverse">
							<p class="body med">When developing a new product, we study not only the cace but also its area for
								a better understanding of what's the most appropriate technical solution we can make. At this
								stage, we form our common vision of the final product and build a general work plan.</p>
							<div class="img-wrapper">
								<img width="488" height="392"
									src="https://www.meme-arsenal.com/memes/6cec25ddda4b0fd41a8c00b57113fdde.jpg" alt="">
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="block-item">
							<p class="body med">Before we start developing, we want you to see how the final product will look.
								We visualize it by designing and building a complete layout so we can make changes due to your
								vision of the project.</p>
							<div class="img-wrapper">
								<img width="488" height="392"
									src="https://www.meme-arsenal.com/memes/6cec25ddda4b0fd41a8c00b57113fdde.jpg" alt="">
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="block-item reverse">
							<p class="body med">Developing, quality assurance and testing. It is important that you understand
								what exactly we do at every stage of development as we are using easy to track systems, so you
								can follow the progress.</p>
							<div class="img-wrapper">
								<img width="488" height="392"
									src="https://www.meme-arsenal.com/memes/6cec25ddda4b0fd41a8c00b57113fdde.jpg" alt="">
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="block-item">
							<p class="body med">After the project is lunched, we can support the project as it is running. We
								can implement changes, upgrades or adding new features.</p>
							<div class="img-wrapper">
								<img width="488" height="392"
									src="https://www.meme-arsenal.com/memes/6cec25ddda4b0fd41a8c00b57113fdde.jpg" alt="">
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
		<!-- @import "main-kit/footer.kit" -->
	</div>
